Crocodile's wife ate the jamun and said it very sweet, where did you get it from? Then crocodile told the whole story about his friend monkey and how he met him. 
:
One fine day crocodile took jamun to his home for his wife.
Once upon a time there lived a monkey on an apple tree beside the bank of river, the crocodile was passing by and he was hungry, so monkey offered jamun to the crocodile and from there they became friends. 

